definition.value: A member of the class of quinazolines that is quinazoline which is substituted at positions 2 and 4 by 2-fluorophenyl and (3-acetamidophenyl)nitrilo groups, respectively.
A 2-oxo monocarboxylic acid that is 2-oxopentanoic acid which is substituted at positions 4 and 5 by hydroxy groups (the 4S-enantiomer).
